io.scanbot.sdk.docprocessing

Interface ProcessingInfoProvider


  • public ProcessingInfoProvider

    Provides Document and Page that should be processed or are already processed.

    Results are wrapped into class DocumentDraft

    See Also:
    Document, Page, class DocumentDraft

    • Method Detail

      • getNotProcessedDocuments

        @NotNull
java.util.Collection<io.scanbot.sdk.entity.DocumentDraft> getNotProcessedDocuments()

        Provides documents which are in principle can be processed further (even if at the moment state of device might not allow it). This includes not processed documents and documents queued for OCR.

        Returns:
        collection of Document and Page which are awaiting to be processed.

      • getProcessedDocuments

        @NotNull
java.util.Collection<io.scanbot.sdk.entity.DocumentDraft> getProcessedDocuments()

        Provides documents which are processed. This includes processed documents and documents queued for OCR.

        Returns:
        collection of Document and Page which are awaiting to be processed.
